comments: Incredibly enthusiastic. Very nice guy willing to work with you to make sure you can do your very best. I loved attending this class.
Very easy to talk to, super fun class. Adam is fantastic, super helpful. Easy easy class as long as you hand in your work, the class practically writes the papers for you.

He makes the class really fun! Always has something interesting and is pretty casual with the class. He makes you feel like you\'re pals. However, he definitely needs to perfect his teaching skills in the way that he is very vague, doesn\'t tell you exactly what is expected on papers. He missed some appointments and is sometimes scatterbrained.
Cogbill is great, a lot of fun, but has high expectations. I hate English and I loved this class. Just do your work though..
